description: At least nine people died when a suspected far-right gunman opened fire on two shisha bars.
title: Germany shooting: What we know about the Hanau attack
title_page: Germany shooting: What we know about the Hanau attack - BBC News
maintext: It is unclear exactly who the victims are. Authorities say they are all aged between 21 and 44, and included both foreigners and German citizens. Among the dead were "several victims of Kurdish origin", the Kon-Med association of Kurds in Germany said.
